 six months\u2019 choice single\npames: 8% per cent for others.\niotais PET reas $1,383 490.669 00\ni\nBOSTON COPPER STOCKS,\ni\nEe\nQuotations furnished by W. B, Hibbs Co..\nmembers of the New York Stock Exchange, Hibbs\nTY o Ww\nM\n\nTE\nBuilding. Bid. Asked.\nBATEREIEG oneesersrsesnsonstrrssnesrensnntsn 3) 7\nButhe Coalition. er sersrasesssrstsssaressonse BB 18%\n59\n35\n66\n\n11%\n14%\n\n2 eR 0;\neee\n\nA RAAT 53\nCoa XH \"eee 0 S\u2014\n2 cress\nFra y\ni ral\nTam TL LLL EET TET TTT 0\nFRSIEY ores ariivsanras mT\nUtah Consclidated............. Saasasisr se 2%\nVictoria Ere AS RAN SASERRETESL ATELIER SS seman 2%\nI I SR ry REE\nsewers tereanes AN] sesrasnersserssese En\n\"es\n\nkn\nSepteml Low. Close.\n13.73 Ld 1355]\nRot Eepaniynegn. tos\nX ja ne Va Sa aT\nA 5 1 i\n1ergen 407 y's strmw\nfirhion\nMichigan *on hi H)\nMohaw\nN B i A\nNorth 1 $i\nOld Dominios sesaee-. 38\n\nUneco a 3% i\nOsceola 3 en RR TNR\nParrott L9\nQ\nBhannbot sessssasennessssses DAR\nNS Lake Lge)\nof Metah\nSuperior Pittsburg i\nBwit 1\n\nGOVERNMENT BONDS,\nBS 13.2 13.2\na I 13 12\nNew York, Sept. 23.\u2014Bid and asked prices on gov\nerument securities:\nBid. Asked.\nw 1 13.29 13.30\nTotal. ARP RRO A OR o 1,128,126 62 lL eg\nFixcess of ordinary receipts...\nTELE sesssrssreene\n9s or ET\n2s, coupon, 1990....... essesressnsnssnsesnses 10K 10134\n3s, registered, 1308-18. ....cvviiiniiicennnns 101K 10283\n\u201c3s, coupon, 1908-18... .cciiiiiiinnniinineens 101% 102%\n4, registered, 1925........ sesennsrne sernrer ig 115%\n23, 1 To to 29%\ni y\nNO\n\n\nPanama Canal J0-30-year 2,\nPanama Canal 1330 year 2s,\nponut Excess of all recelpis.....\n8, 4 a 0% ViBoisivsninnannn cecovee\nrey'd, 19%.. 101%\nreg\u2019d, 1988.. 100%\nk\nLargest Morning Circulation.\n\nCURB JNIARYXET.\nNEW YORK STOCK MARKET.\nQuotations furnished by W. B. Hibbs Co.\nmembers of the New York Stock Exchange, Hibbs\n\nCall money: Open, 1%; high, 2; low, 1%; close, 2.\nSAI OF QEHAREY BBY HOURS\n\nDeverrarsrarsassssssansssnsssssanns\